{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/projects/designsystem/","webpackCompilationHash":"","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"cb4dae9c-f25e-54f0-be3f-12e86678db1c","excerpt":"…","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/78b4e00bf950bd9bff1cabd78918a7b3/0d938/overview.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52.95343988881167%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"overview\"\n        title=\"overview\"\n        src=\"/static/78b4e00bf950bd9bff1cabd78918a7b3/e49a9/overview.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/78b4e00bf950bd9bff1cabd78918a7b3/8d449/overview.png 160w,\n/static/78b4e00bf950bd9bff1cabd78918a7b3/01387/overview.png 320w,\n/static/78b4e00bf950bd9bff1cabd78918a7b3/e49a9/overview.png 640w,\n/static/78b4e00bf950bd9bff1cabd78918a7b3/f570d/overview.png 960w,\n/static/78b4e00bf950bd9bff1cabd78918a7b3/0309e/overview.png 1280w,\n/static/78b4e00bf950bd9bff1cabd78918a7b3/0d938/overview.png 2878w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>设计系统自诞生以来备受追捧，那么设计系统究竟是什么呢？它又是为了解决什么问题呢？</p>\n<p>很多人认为设计系统就是一个可复用的组件库，这是对设计系统最大的误解，组件库只是它的产出物之一。在我看来，设计系统是为了提高设计和开发协作效率而出现的。它不仅仅包含组件库，还包含了设计规范、协作模式以及一系列的自动化工具等等。设计系统的构建者也不仅仅是设计师，团队内所有设计系统的使用者都可以参与其中。</p>\n<p>鉴于国内相关的资料不多，我建了这个网站来收集相关的教程、文章、书籍和案例，希望帮助更多人了解并运用设计系统。如果你想要参与其中，可以到 <a href=\"https://github.com/leadream/designsystem/issues\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Github 仓库</a>提交 issue。</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"设计系统","date":"2015/06/30","description":"收集设计系统相关的教程、文章、书籍和案例。","color":"#FFF","cover":"designsystem.jpg","demo":"https://designsystem.cc","demoText":null}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/projects/designsystem/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/projects/designtools/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"设计工具集"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/tools/movielect/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"选个电影小程序"}}}}}